<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/19974892">实践是检验真理的唯一标准吗？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="169931" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"></div>


