</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$zengjuchen" href="/people/zengjuchen">曾举臣</a>，<strong title="本人已准备好接受任何善意" class="zu-question-my-bio">本人已准备好接受任何善意</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="2">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$lllllustrator" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/lllllustrator" class="zg-link" title="lllllustrator">lllllustrator</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户</span>
</span>


<span>赞同</span>


</div>
